 lucid style will make the book accessible to a wider readership.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aMotion picturesxAesthetics. 0aMotion picturesxEvaluation. 4aFilm and Media Studies 2019. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh  aaesthetics.  aanalysis.  acinema.  aclose reading.  aclose-reading.  aevaluation.  afilm.  aform.  amedium.  apattern.  astyle.1 aKlevan, Andrew, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 2018 eBook-Packagez978311128277040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978152613256740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781526132567423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781526132567/original  a978-3-11-128277-0  Manchester University Press 2018 eBook-Packageb2018  aGBV-deGruyter-alles